properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Fernandina Beach to St. Augustine FL out 20 NM; Coastal waters from St. Augustine to Flagler Beach FL out 20 NM; Coastal waters from Altamaha Sound to Fernandina Beach FL out 20 NM
properties.headline: Marine Weather Statement issued January 14 at 10:12AM EST by NWS Jacksonville FL
properties.description:
Patchy to areas of fog will continue to impact portions of the nearshore
coastal waters, including some estuaries and some waterways. Local
visibilities of around 1 mile or less will be possible. Fog may
re-develop and become widespread tonight.

Mariners who approach areas of fog are urged to reduce speed, and
keep a lookout for other vessels, buoys, and breakwaters. Keep
your navigation lights on.

NWSheadline: AREAS OF FOG ALONG THE COAST THROUGH MIDDAY
